{"lastModified":1751636944411,"uri":"c::8276484364::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Italy, Sardinia\n\nALTVS is a 29.90m / 98ft Motor Superyacht built in 2020 by Amer and later underwent a refit in 2024. Sleeping 10 guests in 5 cabins and with a crew of 5. Cruising at 23.00 kn/ph with a top speed of 30.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise a Master cabin with en-suite bathroom facilities, 2 VIP cabins with double beds and en-suite bathroom facilities, and 2 double cabins with double (convertible) beds and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"ALTVS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0::assets::2736d850-299f-11f0-82a3-4754badd2f6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0::assets::279a7c20-299f-11f0-82a3-4754badd2f6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0::assets::272461c0-299f-11f0-82a3-4754badd2f6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0::assets::26f0f5b0-299f-11f0-82a3-4754badd2f6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0::assets::27106490-299f-11f0-82a3-4754badd2f6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0::assets::276e8a20-299f-11f0-82a3-4754badd2f6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0::assets::275bec80-299f-11f0-82a3-4754badd2f6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0::assets::277f7a10-299f-11f0-82a3-4754badd2f6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0::assets::274cd150-299f-11f0-82a3-4754badd2f6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4bafb9f0-9155-11ef-ae28-db98f755ffe0::assets::27893e10-299f-11f0-82a3-4754badd2f6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4b